EU Imposes Weapons Embargo on Syria as Country Uses Force to Stem Uprising

-- B y   J o h n   M a r t e n s
-- 
2011-05-09T18:29:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-09/eu-imposes-weapons-embargo-on-syria-as-country-uses-force-to-stem-uprising.html
The European Union imposed an embargo
on exports to  Syria  of arms and equipment as well as a visa ban
and assets freeze targeting 13 Syrian officials and their
associates who have been identified as being responsible for
repression against the nation’s civilian population.  Details of the decision and the list of persons subject to
the restrictive measures will be published on May 10, the
European Union’s council in Brussels said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Martens at 
 jmartens1@bloomberg.net  